      <ul>
        <h1>Welcome to Nebulas Fables</h1>
        <br>
        <li>We are an interactive learning zone made to help you understand the intricacies of the stars.</li>
        <br>
        <li>Our site is dedicated to teaching about star clusters, constellations, and cultural interpretations of the galaxy.</li>
        <br>
        <li>While our page is still in the development stages, we are planning to expand from simply offering links and images of the stars into a fully functioning star chart with an interactive database.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
