        <li>Visit our NASA button</li>
        <li>Once there, try typing your favorite constellation into the search bar!</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div id="Myth">
      <h2>Mythos</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Coming Soon!</li>
        <br>
        <li>Our next planned installment for our page is to add a mythology database, filled with fun facts about different mythologies connected to the stars.</li>
        <br>
        <li>Each mythology will have a dedicated star chart, regional mode, culture filter, and map function that will allow you to search the world for where the myths are derived from.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div id="Direct">
      <h2>Directory</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Following the creation of the Mythos database, a helpful directory filled with potential searches, varying lists of what can be learned, and other fun interactive opportunities will be added to the directory.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
